## Availability Blueprints
Blueprints
  # The main API availability SLO
  "api_availability" success_rate(test):
    Requiring { env: String }
    signals { vendor: "datadog" }

##  === Latency Blueprints ===
# These blueprints track latency
Blueprints
  "api_latency" success_rate(test):
    Requiring { env: String }
    signals { vendor: "datadog" }
